I"Šç<h1 id="components-from-scratch">Components From Scratch</h1>
<hr />
<p><img src="images/js.gif" alt="airBnB" /></p>

<hr />

<p>Components are a great way to design and develop your UI using smaller, reusable pieces with better consistency.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>In todayâ€™s ecosystem, UI components can also function as UX components, combining the power to create both functional and visual consistency.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>You can design some compenents, then reuse them to build your <em>own product very quickly</em>. So letâ€™s <em>design</em>!</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><em>Most of the components have a dependency on <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/">Bootstrap (4.3)</a> &amp; <a href="https://fontawesome.com/">Fontawesome (5.7)</a>, so make sure you have the libraries in your project.</em></p>
</blockquote>

<h4 id="avatar">Avatar:</h4>

<p>So letâ€™s begin with a simple one, useful for your <em>profile</em> for example.</p>

<p><img class="avatar" alt="avatar" src="https://kitt.lewagon.com/placeholder/users/cveneziani" />
<img class="avatar-large" alt="avatar-large" src="https://kitt.lewagon.com/placeholder/users/arthur-littm" />
